interactivity.requirements: You must have seen or permanently missed the following Events: Seen Main Events up to " Lifting the Curse "
interactivity.to_get_this_event: Visit the Koi Cafe at night

progression.synopsis: Sensei visits the Koi Cafe in the evening, and finds that Molly works there too. Sensei is surprised that someone as high-energy as Molly has been put in a position of responsibility. Molly ends up talking about her expertise with dating sims, and why they're better than real life. Sensei manages to get a drink eventually, although Molly shares Rin 's policy of inventing her own.

changelog: This Event was added in Update 0.7.
